reviewText: Came in good condition but unfortunately i have to return because i misunderstood&thought it was a dvd not blue ray:(

I've gotten all of the main three Chipmunk movies. I must say...that Alvin and the Chipmunks #1 brought many memories for childhood, but Chipwrecked Three gave me and my 3 year niece great pleause and many laughs. We've watched it many times. I would recommend this movie to an parents that are looking for something for family night.
